    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my reliable ride! It\u2019s been so good to me and is in really wonderful shape for its next owner. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is super smooth and ready to hit the road. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s looking sharp and running just like it should. Come take it for a spin\u2014I know you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
