    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is mechanically sound, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a recently refreshed suspension utilizing Bilstein dampers to maintain the platform's signature handling dynamics. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and VANOS system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust and the hydraulic steering rack provides the precise, communicative feedback enthusiasts demand. It sits on genuine staggered Style 67 wheels with Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. 55,000 miles. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Minor cosmetic wear on rear bumper. Mechanically sound.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
