    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish with only minor road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free environment; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, while all power features, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is solid. It has a documented service history, including a recent fluid service and multi-point inspection. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires provide excellent grip with plenty of life left. It has been garage-kept and treated with respect, offering the next owner a reliable, comfortable, and sharp-looking ride that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
