    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with its next owner. Come take it for a spin, I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
