    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2008 Corvette Z06 is a purist's machine, powered by the legendary 7.0L LS7 V8 featuring a dry-sump oiling system, titanium connecting rods, and a 7,000 RPM redline. The hydroformed aluminum chassis and magnesium roof structure provide a rigid, lightweight platform, while the Tremec TR-6060 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile gear selection. This example retains its factory-engineered carbon fiber composite fenders and floor panels, ensuring a superior power-to-weight ratio. Equipped with the FE4 performance suspension and massive six-piston front monoblock calipers, the mechanical integrity of this Z06 is sorted and track-ready. A well-maintained driver's car with excellent throttle response and visceral feedback.",
